#, no-c-format
msgid "A player declares he has no choice but to play dangerous game"
msgstr "Igralec izjavi, da nima druge izbire, kot da igra nevarno igro"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tiles options"
msgstr "Možnosti ploščic"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Tileset selector</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbirnik nabora ploščic</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Tileset selector</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbirnik nabora ploščic</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Tiles</guilabel> selector to select graphics for the tiles."
msgstr ""
"Z izbirnikom <guilabel>Ploščice</guilabel> izberite grafiko za ploščice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background options"
msgstr "Možnosti ozadja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Background selector</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbirnik ozadja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Background selector</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbirnik ozadja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Background</guilabel> selector to select a background "
"graphic for the game."
msgstr ""
"Z izbirnikom <guilabel>Ozadje</guilabel> izberite grafiko ozadja za igro."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some backgrounds like the Chinese Landscape need some time to load. If you "
"feel that the program should start faster or that resizing the main window "
"takes too long, you might try some other background."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera ozadja, kot je kitajska pokrajina, potrebujejo nekaj časa za "
"nalaganje. Če menite, da bi se program moral zagnati hitreje ali da "
"spreminjanje velikosti glavnega okna traja predolgo, lahko poskusite z "
"drugim ozadjem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Ruleset Editor</title>"
msgstr "<title>Urejevalnik nabora pravil</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Ruleset Editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejevalnik nabora pravil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Ruleset Editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejevalnik nabora pravil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Ruleset Editor to customize rulesets. Predefined rulesets are shown "
"in an italic font, customized rulesets have a normal font. Predefined "
"rulesets cannot be changed by the user in any way, however an update of "
"&kajongg; might. Customized rulesets will never be affected by an update."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite urejevalnik nabora pravil za prilagajanje nabora pravil. Vnaprej "
"določeni nabori pravil so prikazani v poševni pisavi, prilagojeni nabori "
"pravil pa imajo običajno pisavo. Vnaprej določenih naborov pravil uporabnik "
"ne more spremeniti na noben način, vendar posodobitev &kajongg; morda. "
"Posodobitev nikoli ne bo vplivala na prilagojene nabore pravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting a new game, you will be able to select a ruleset for that "
"game. All rulesets defined in the ruleset editor can be used. The ruleset is "
"saved together with the game, so you can always change rulesets here - your "
"changes will only affect future games."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete novo igro, boste lahko izbrali nabor pravil za to igro. Uporabijo "
"se lahko vsi nabori pravil, definirani v urejevalniku nabora pravil. Nabor "
"pravil je shranjen skupaj z igro, tako da lahko tukaj vedno spremenite "
"nabore pravil - vaše spremembe bodo vplivale samo na prihodnje igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule, Points, x2, Limits"
msgstr "Pravilo, točke, x2, meje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply double click on whatever you want to change. If all values are "
"cleared, this rule will have no influence on the game. Rules cannot be "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto dvakrat kliknite na tisto, kar želite spremeniti. Če so vse "
"vrednosti izbrisane, to pravilo ne bo imelo vpliva na igro. Pravil ni mogoče "
"izbrisati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy and Remove"
msgstr "Kopiraj in odstrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can copy and remove entire rulesets."
msgstr "Lahko kopirate in odstranite celotne nize pravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Again this can even be done if existing games use this ruleset since every "
"game has its own ruleset copy. You can view rulesets for old games: <link "
"linkend=\"game-menu-scoreGame\">Load</link> the old game and <link linkend="
"\"view-explain-scores\">show its score table</link>."
msgstr ""
"Tudi to je mogoče narediti, če obstoječe igre uporabljajo ta nabor pravil, "
"saj ima vsaka igra svojo kopijo nabora pravil. Ogledate si lahko nabore "
"pravil za stare igre: <link linkend=\"game-menu-scoreGame\">Naložite</link> "
"staro igro in <link linkend=\"view-explain-scores\">prikažite njeno tabelo "
"rezultatov</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compare"
msgstr "Primerjaj"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Ruleset Comparator</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Primerjalnik nabora pravil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Ruleset Comparator</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Primerjalnik nabora pravil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select this command when an entire ruleset is selected. It lets you "
"compare the selected ruleset against any other ruleset."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz lahko izberete, ko je izbran celoten nabor pravil. Omogoča "
"primerjavo izbranega nabora pravil s katerim koli drugim naborom pravil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Keybindings"
msgstr "Privzete vezave tipk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
