msgstr "Celozaslonski način."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid "Known problems"
msgstr "Znane težave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid "In playing mode, penalties are not yet possible."
msgstr "V načinu igranja kazni še niso možne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:934
#, no-c-format
msgid "The computer players are still rather stupid."
msgstr "Računalniški igralci so še vedno precej neumni."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:938
#, no-c-format
msgid "Possible future features"
msgstr "Možne funkcije v prihodnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add more rulesets. This should optionally be done by people using those "
"rulesets regularly."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte več naborov pravil. To bi po želji morali storiti ljudje, ki redno "
"uporabljajo te nabore pravil."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the way &kajongg; looks use the menubar to open the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">configuration utility</link>."
msgstr ""
"Da Če želite spremeniti način &kajongg; videza uporabite menijsko vrstico, "
"da odprete <link linkend=\"configuration\">konfiguracijski pripomoček</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to assign tiles to players?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabim tipkovnico za dodeljevanje ploščic igralcem?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. See <link linkend=\"enterhand-tiles\">Have &kajongg; compute the score</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Da. Glejte <link linkend=\"enterhand-tiles\">Naj &kajongg; izračuna "
"rezultat</link>."

